{"featured_counts":0,"common_counts":55,"collapsed_counts":0,"reviewing_counts":0,"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/563667762/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=5\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/563667762/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=3\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","totals":12},"data":[{"id":568317425,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/568317425","content":"答主没有意识到的问题是，做学术是一步一个脚印踏踏实实的学上来的，没有捷径可走，连基本的对前人的工作都没有调研过，那就是对整个问题缺乏一个基本的认识和定位，正所谓“不知者不惧”，这种定位的缺失导致的自大是非常致命的。至于偶然恰好发现了某个解答这点呢，我知道大家都很熟悉也喜欢“牛顿被苹果砸到发现万有引力定律”这种极具戏剧性的发展，然而这种故事只在小说家笔下才会有，并不可信。当然，我承认谁都没法下定论说这个高中生就一定是错的，但是他真的证明出来的概率基本就是0，尤其是在我们了解到这个个高中生本身的数学实力还很一般的情况下（如果是IMO金牌那说不定可能性会高一些），也就是说，这个高中生极大概率下是并没有真的证明出来的，那么我们自然有这个义务纠正他，防止他走上“民科”的歧途，你说对吗？当然，如果最后他的证明通过同行评议被接受，别说清华北大了的入学了，直接拿个荣誉教授都有可能对吧，但这个点的概率恐怕比他买彩票中奖还要小呀。","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1546264914,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"c003e41ea3ef1b3bfedb62ce3a006084","url_token":"chan-chingky","name":"Amadeus Chan","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-60884fbd81fdc581913d3f5b16e17d91_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-60884fbd81fdc581913d3f5b16e17d91_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/c003e41ea3ef1b3bfedb62ce3a006084","user_type":"people","headline":"CS Tsinghua","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":5,"voting":false,"disliked":false,"censor_status":0,"child_comme